This paper is primarily focused on the topic of distributing neural network training, which falls under the category of machine learning (cs.LG). The paper also discusses the use of Gossip-like protocols, which is a topic related to distributed computing (cs.DC) and distributed systems (cs.DS). Additionally, the paper evaluates the proposed approach using empirical experiments, which falls under the category of neural networks (cs.NE) and control systems (cs.SY).
